{"id": "1222504574548574301", "channel_id": "1222164364245860483", "type": 0, "author_id": "848454386598412318", "author_name": "ruko9999", "author_bot": false, "content": "就 現在貓貓的蟾蜍湯\n就是沒有保留的預備1", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T11:16:43.609000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222164364245860483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🪡🦉：原创唤醒体（1）—第（1）次投稿", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359914895646811"]}
{"id": "1222508831662149633", "channel_id": "1222164364245860483", "type": 19, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "我這個有考量到，所以削弱戰鬥中的回血效果，且讓覺醒卡費用變三費。以1200血為例，開覺醒就相當於至少回99血，不然三費卡按理來說要是一費或兩費", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T11:33:38.584000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-27T11:33:46.239000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["848454386598412318"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1222499033424330762", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222164364245860483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🪡🦉：原创唤醒体（1）—第（1）次投稿", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359914895646811"]}
