{"id": "1222509456987000873", "channel_id": "1222164364245860483", "type": 0, "author_id": "733514425847513171", "author_name": "xuan4185", "author_bot": false, "content": "寫棄掉就生效是因為那個預備真的很鳥，它必須要是回合結束時被棄掉才會降費", "timestamp": "2024-03-27T11:36:07.673000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1222164364245860483", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "🪡🦉：原创唤醒体（1）—第（1）次投稿", "forum_channel_id": "1174185304027045969", "thread_tags": ["1182359773723754537", "1182359914895646811"]}
